message: Hi Bob, I understand the value of this product to you, but I must ensure it meets my minimum value requirements. I'm offering the product for $1800000.
Hi Alice, I appreciate your offer, but it's beyond my budget. I'm willing to go up to $900000 for the product. Let me know if this works for you.
Hi Bob, I appreciate your interest, but I can't go as low as $900000. Considering our positions, would you consider $1650000?
Hi Alice, I understand your position, but $1650000 is still too high for me. I'm willing to increase my offer to $950000. Can we meet somewhere in the middle?
